Runtime
  Handles animations and user events and calls the appropriate mode handlers.

Mode Handlers
  One for each mode: RUN, EVAL, LRN, LST_* etc.
  They handle key presses and next() calls.

Parser
  Used by RUN, EVAL and LRN mode handlers to transform key presses and program
  steps into structured operations.

Operation Evaluators
  One for each operation (lnx, sto, gto, ...). They transform the calculator
  state.
